WEBVTT

00:00.096 --> 00:02.764
<i>???</i>

00:02.832 --> 00:04.266
And tomorrow, you talk to Adrian.

00:04.333 --> 00:07.335
Whatever she decides to do about... this...

00:07.403 --> 00:10.071
- is her decision.
- I want you to tell Amy,

00:10.139 --> 00:11.473
and I want you to be as kind to Adrian...

00:11.541 --> 00:13.808
as you were to Amy when she was in this situation.

00:13.876 --> 00:15.176
Are you sure everything's okay?

00:16.412 --> 00:17.779
I told my dad.

00:17.847 --> 00:19.314
You promised me you'd give me a couple of days.

00:19.382 --> 00:21.383
If Amy wants to go to a music program in New York,

00:21.450 --> 00:22.851
<i>you should encourage her to do that.</i>

00:22.919 --> 00:24.319
Why? So she won't find out?

00:24.387 --> 00:25.887
I want to offer Adrian my help...

00:25.955 --> 00:27.489
by offering her some options.

00:27.557 --> 00:29.724
Why don't you just focus on you and your own life?

00:29.792 --> 00:31.993
I'm thinking I might get married.

00:32.061 --> 00:34.029
When you say you want to get married,

00:34.096 --> 00:35.797
you do mean to Tammy, don't you?

00:35.865 --> 00:37.966
You're absolutely sure you can find a place?

00:38.034 --> 00:39.701
If nothing else, Ricky said I could stay there.

00:39.769 --> 00:40.969
I think you need parents around.

00:41.037 --> 00:41.970
Then I'll stay with Coach.

00:42.038 --> 00:43.138
Something is going on.

00:43.205 --> 00:44.339
Not really.

00:44.407 --> 00:45.640
Something's going on with me.

00:45.708 --> 00:46.942
We're just gonna let her go to New York?

00:47.009 --> 00:48.310
I don't think we have a choice.

00:48.377 --> 00:50.278
I can't tell her,

00:50.346 --> 00:52.247
- not before she takes off.
- Which is when?

00:52.315 --> 00:53.281
Tomorrow.

00:53.349 --> 00:54.649
What's the matter?

00:54.717 --> 00:56.284
Adrian's pregnant.

